- quay.io/condaforge/linux-anvil-x86_64:alma9

    min_pin: x.x

about.summary: Support functions,  data sets, and vignettes for the 'psych' package. Contains several of the biggest data sets for the 'psych' package as well as one vignette. Support functions,  data sets, and vignettes for the 'psych' package. Contains several of the biggest data sets for the 'psych' package as well as one vignette. A few helper functions for file manipulation are included as well. For more information, see the <https://personality-project.org/r/> web page.

name: r-psychtools
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "2.5.7.22" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-psychtools
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/psychTools_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/psychTools/psychTools_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: adfab961a8743d91cba9d2b29f7ad774758c26e8dfe3bc4739165c6dd650bfb1

build:
  number: 1
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
    - cross-r-base {{ r_base }}    # [build_platform != target_platform]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-foreign
    - r-psych
    - r-rtf
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-foreign
    - r-psych
    - r-rtf

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('psychTools')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('psychTools')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://personality-project.org/r/psych/ https://personality-project.org/r/psych-manual.pdf
  license: GPL-2.0-or-later
  summary: Support functions,  data sets, and vignettes for the 'psych' package. Contains several of the biggest data sets for the 'psych' package as well as one vignette. A few helper functions for file manipulation are included as well. For more information, see the <https://personality-project.org/r/> web page.
  license_family: GPL2
  license_file:
    - {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - izahn
